  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nCurrently blobs are stored for 4096 epochs ~18 days (`MIN_EPOCHS_FOR_BLOB_SIDECARS_REQUESTS`) before they are pruned according to the spec. It would be good have a flag (hidden?) that allows extending this, as it'd be useful to retain blobs for a longer period of time for testing / debugging. ",
